  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Install and use @phosphor-icons/react for all iconography to maintain a professional, consistent weight.",
    "Implement the UI in pt-BR language as requested.",
    "Ensure all data tables (Recordings, Agents) use Shadcn UI with strict borders and dense padding, matching the 'Control Room' grid philosophy.",
    "KPI values MUST use a monospace font (JetBrains Mono or similar) for readability of telemetry data.",
    "Add data-testid attributes to all interactive elements for testing.",
    "Avoid generic purple/teal gradients. Stick to strict grayscale with semantic colors (red/green/blue) indicating system/agent states.",
    "For the Recordings view, implement an inline or bottom-docked audio player for playback.",
    "Use standard grid patterns for the Dashboard: primary metrics at the top (col-span-1), charts taking wider spaces, and list of online agents on the side (col-span-1 row-span-2)."
  ]
}